# 프로젝트 루트에서
nano .gitattributes
# 또는
code .gitattributes
```

**내용:**
```
# Auto detect text files and normalize to LF
* text=auto eol=lf

# Python files
*.py text eol=lf

# YAML files
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf

# Docker files
Dockerfile text eol=lf
docker-compose*.yml text eol=lf

# Shell scripts
*.sh text eol=lf

# Windows files
*.bat text eol=crlf